[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0921","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0921.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1074","title":"Webmin 暴力破解权限提升漏洞","description":"Webmin 0.5 之前版本存在登录认证缺陷，未对针对有效用户名的密码尝试次数进行限制。远程攻击者可利用此漏洞对已知用户名实施暴力破解攻击，通过大量尝试弱口令或字典密码获取系统管理员权限。该漏洞影响 Webmin 早期版本，攻击无需任何前置条件，且可远程触发，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1074"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.017","remediation":"升级 Webmin 至 0.5 或更高版本，该版本已限制同一用户名下的无效密码尝试次数。作为临时缓解措施，可配置 fail2ban 规则对 Webmin 登录接口进行频率限制，或通过防火墙限制可访问 Webmin 管理端口的来源 IP 范围。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/9138","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/98","http://www.webmin.com/webmin/changes.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0921.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0921.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0921.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0890","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0890.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1042","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9130,\"outputTokens\":26,\"totalTokens\":10820}}","description":"Cisco Resource Manager (CRM) 1.0 与 1.1 版本在运行过程中会创建具有全局可读权限（world-readable）的日志文件及临时文件，导致本地用户可读取到其中存储的敏感信息。由于文件权限配置不当，任何具有本地系统访问权限的用户均可直接读取这些文件，从而泄露用户标识（User ID）、明文密码以及 SNMP 团体字符串（community string）等凭据。该漏洞影响范围限于已安装上述版本 CRM 且存在本地账户的 Cisco 设备，攻击者无需特殊权限，仅需以普通本地用户身份访问文件系统即可利用，属于典型的信息泄露类本地漏洞。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1042"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:35.067","remediation":"建议升级至 Cisco Resource Manager 1.2 或更高版本（已修复文件权限问题），或将现有 CRM 1.0/1.1 的日志与临时文件目录权限修改为 600（仅所有者可读写）。若无法升级，请限制本地账号访问权限，并迁移至 CiscoWorks 等受支持的网络管理平台。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/crmtmp-pub.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/49836c1c79a31c6cbe258de560530ef5be1db5f4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1042","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1042.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ae10aeb9b17952d60531f6bc06df8547d2b0b568/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qqff-qxc6-9qw5/GHSA-qqff-qxc6-9qw5.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87012/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1042.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/70290debf97c1057397e6f7c8c733dec0658bf76/1999.tsv","https://github.com/kookaip/PhD-ICSE2023-PrivacyVulnerabilities/blob/f07e7ceba63e856fe3d9dd40cee793b0ef452153/replication-package/data/7-cve-coder2.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0890.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0889","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0889.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1035","title":"Microsoft IIS 3.0/4.0 HTTP GET 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 3.0 和 4.0 在 x86 和 Alpha 平台上存在 HTTP GET 拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送畸形的 HTTP GET 请求触发该漏洞，导致 IIS 服务挂起停止响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行在 x86 和 Alpha 处理器架构上的 IIS 3.0 和 4.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程发送畸形 GET 请求触发漏洞，导致 Web 服务停止响应。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 5.0，属于中危级别拒绝服务漏洞，微软已发布补丁修复该漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1035"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:34.207","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-019 的安全补丁（KB234905），修复 IIS 3.0/4.0 对畸形 HTTP GET 请求处理不当导致的拒绝服务漏洞。若无法立即打补丁，可在 IIS 管理器中删除 .HTR、.IDC、.STM 等不需要的脚本映射，或在防火墙层面过滤包含畸形请求行的 HTTP 请求作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q192/2/96.asp","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-019","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1823","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1035.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c7dbcfe83bb4dc502ef05181d3fc65159afa615a/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1035.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1035","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/fb79aaf8eeeb3ec551114292cd7a8693e166aee6/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1035.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1035.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6da213119b3c54637329347c0dc42c66b8a84f0a/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rpfw-6596-9q7g/GHSA-rpfw-6596-9q7g.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1035.yaml","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1035.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0889.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0579","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0579.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0815","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 SNMP Agent 内存泄露拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 SP5 之前版本的 SNMP 代理存在内存泄漏漏洞，远程未经身份认证的攻击者可向目标系统发送大量 SNMP 查询请求，导致 SNMP 代理进程内存持续耗尽，最终引发拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 SP5 之前的所有版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程发起攻击，仅需向目标发送大量 SNMP 查询请求即可耗尽系统内存资源导致服务拒绝，CVSS 评分 5.0，属中危拒绝服务漏洞。Microsoft 已在 Windows NT 4.0 SP5 中修复此漏洞，建议升级至 SP5 或更高版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0815"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.917","remediation":"建议升级至 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 5 或更高版本以修复 SNMP Agent 内存泄漏漏洞。若无法立即升级，可通过服务管理器禁用 SNMP 服务（snmp.exe）或在防火墙层面阻断 UDP 161 端口作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/support/kb/articles/q196/2/70.asp","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1974","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A952","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0815.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/df06113bb625f86b49f1950d55874a29f8e76a55/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0815.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0815","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0815.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0815.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-hj67-mggc-gx7v/GHSA-hj67-mggc-gx7v.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0815.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0579.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0572","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0572.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0808","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":10240,\"inputTokens\":563,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10820}}","description":"ISC DHCP Distribution 服务器（dhcpd）1.0 和 2.0 版本中存在多个缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送超长 DHCP 选项字段触发溢出，导致服务崩溃拒绝服务，甚至可能在服务器上执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行易受版本 DHCP 服务的系统，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，属高危漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0808"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-12-31T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.993","remediation":"建议立即升级至 ISC DHCP 3.0.1 及以上版本，或迁移至 ISC Kea DHCP 等现代维护版本。若暂时无法升级，请在防火墙层面限制仅允许受信任网段访问 UDP 67/68 端口，并在 dhcpd.conf 中限制 max-lease-time 与 option 长度作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-053.shtml","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221101925960&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5b55afba6f3a87fe9319e1de76170e4c2760d614/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0808.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0808","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0808.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0808.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-q75m-w275-jrg5/GHSA-q75m-w275-jrg5.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88362/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0808.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0572.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1989","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1989.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1547","title":"web_listener 认证绕过漏洞","description":"web_listener 是一款用于监听网络连接的工具。该工具存在认证绕过漏洞，攻击者可在未提供有效凭证的情况下访问本应受保护的监听端口或管理功能，从而读取、重定向或干扰经过该监听器的网络流量。攻击只需能够与目标监听器建立网络连接即可发起，无需用户交互。厂商已确认该问题并提供了修复版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1547"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"1999-12-31","remediation":"升级 web_listener 到官方发布的修复版本，并限制监听器仅绑定到受信任的内部网络接口，同时配置访问控制列表以校验连接来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T01:56:03.118420473+00:00","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1547","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-1547"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1989.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1908","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1908.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1474","title":"Microsoft PowerPoint 程序自动运行漏洞","description":"Microsoft PowerPoint 95 及 97 版本存在程序自动运行漏洞。当用户通过 Internet Explorer 等浏览器打开 PowerPoint 文档时，攻击者可在幻灯片放映模式下触发应用程序自动执行，而无需用户确认交互。该漏洞允许远程攻击者在未授权情况下利用浏览器与 PowerPoint 的集成机制，绕过安全提示直接启动应用程序，可能导致任意代码执行。CVSS v2.0 评分为 7.5，危害等级高，影响范围广泛。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1474"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"1999-12-31","remediation":"升级至 Office 2000 SR-1 及以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，在 PowerPoint 中依次点击「工具」→「宏」→「安全性」，将安全级别设为「高」；同时禁用 ActiveX 控件自动执行，在注册表 `HKEY_CURRENT_USER\\Software\\Microsoft\\Office\\<版本>\\PowerPoint\\Options` 下新建 DWORD 值 `AutoRun` 并设为 0。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1908.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1410","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1410.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1218","title":"Netscape Enterprise Server 早期版本 CGI 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Netscape Enterprise Server 部分早期版本在处理 CGI 请求时存在信息泄露缺陷，攻击者可构造特殊请求获取服务器内部路径或环境变量等敏感信息，进而辅助后续攻击。该漏洞无需认证，远程即可触发，影响运行在默认配置下的 Web 服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1218"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"1999-12-31","remediation":"升级到 Netscape Enterprise Server 修复版本，或在服务器配置中限制 CGI 目录访问并禁用不必要的 CGI 脚本暴露。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1218"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1410.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1210","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1210.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1592","title":"SunOS sendmail 5 未指定安全漏洞","description":"SunOS 4.1.3_U1 与 4.1.4 操作系统随附的 sendmail 5 邮件传输代理中存在多处未具体说明的安全漏洞。由于漏洞细节未公开，确切的触发机制与攻击向量尚不清晰，但 NVD 将其 CVSS 评分定为 7.5（高危）。攻击者可能通过网络向目标邮件服务发送特制请求或邮件，潜在影响包括拒绝服务或权限提升。运行上述 SunOS 版本的邮件服务器均可能受影响，建议尽快评估并部署补丁。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1592"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-07-17","remediation":"升级 sendmail 至 8.x 或更高版本，或应用 Sun 提供的安全补丁（Sun Patch ID 100159 等）；若无法立即升级，应限制 sendmail 网络监听地址并关闭无关 SMTP 功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/search/document.do?assetkey=1-22-00159-1","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/243","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a23c9152c0ce51f4625e88e1e6abe715ca2d7579/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1592.json","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-1592"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1210.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1204","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1204.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1587","title":"Sun Solaris 8/9 /usr/ucb/ps 本地信息泄露漏洞","description":"Solaris 8 和 9 系统中的 /usr/ucb/ps 工具存在本地信息泄露漏洞。本地攻击者通过执行该程序可获取系统敏感信息，包括其他用户进程的详细信息、内存布局等，可能导致进一步权限提升。该漏洞影响 Solaris 8 和 9 版本，攻击者需拥有本地 shell 访问权限，无需特殊权限即可触发。利用方式简单，直接运行 /usr/ucb/ps 命令即可泄露本不应被普通用户访问的进程信息。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1587"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"1999-12-31","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 102215（Solaris 8/9 对应补丁 ID 102215-xx），或升级到受支持的最新 Solaris 版本。如无法打补丁，可移除 `/usr/ucb/ps` 的 setuid 权限（`chmod 555 /usr/ucb/ps`）并改用标准 `/usr/bin/ps` 替代，同时限制可登录用户为受信任管理员。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/2242","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-1587.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2218edc43f34225d168835de417dff40749bef5/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1587.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1587","https://github.com/vulncheck-oss/0day.today.archive/blob/3664abdd71985a44aff3260896a8f36e2f4a9682/local-exploits/26267.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2119b082f4927b0a9c902ed9fe95efb3b301cb81/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1587.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1587.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vrp4-j3rg-w647/GHSA-vrp4-j3rg-w647.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/S/solaris9_120240.nasl","https://github.com/cjac/NIST-NVD/blob/54a2c240455f1a25d6d620bf5d9ff1d0533949cb/lib/NIST/NVD/Query.pm","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2007/CVE-2007-0805.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1204.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1203","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1203.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1586","title":"SunOS 4.1.x loadmodule 程序环境变量处理本地提权漏洞","description":"SunOS 4.1.x 系统中的 loadmodule 程序（被 xnews 等调用）在启动过程中未能正确清理（sanitize）其运行环境变量，导致本地用户可通过构造恶意的环境变量来操纵程序行为。由于 loadmodule 通常以较高权限运行，本地已登录的普通用户可利用该环境处理缺陷实现权限提升，获取 root 或其他特权账户的权限。该漏洞影响运行 SunOS 4.1.x 版本且使用 loadmodule 的相关系统，攻击前提是攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，无需远程网络即可完成利用，属于本地权限提升类漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1586"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到已修复该问题的 SunOS 补丁版本，或应用厂商针对 loadmodule 环境变量处理缺陷的安全补丁；在不便升级时，限制对 loadmodule 及 xnews 等调用程序的访问权限，避免不可信本地用户执行该程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-1995-12.html","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/g-02.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/498"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1203.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1136","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1136.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1497","title":"Shiva 远程访问服务器 默认账户弱口令未授权访问","description":"Shiva 远程访问服务器（Shiva Access Manager / LanRover）在默认安装时存在弱口令或未授权访问缺陷，攻击者可在未提供有效凭据的情况下远程连接并获取设备的管理访问权限，进而控制拨号接入网络、读取或修改配置。该漏洞利用条件为设备暴露在可网络访问的范围内且未修改默认凭证，属于因默认配置不当导致的高危认证绕过问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1497"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"1999-12-31","remediation":"修改 Shiva 远程访问服务器的所有默认账户口令，禁用不必要的远程管理访问，配置 ACL 限制管理接口仅允许受信任 IP 访问，并将设备固件/软件升级至厂商发布的安全版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-1999-1497","https://www.securityfocus.com/bid/880/info"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1136.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1136.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1136.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1118","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1118.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1464","title":"Cisco IOS 分布式快速交换访问控制列表绕过漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 11.1CC 及 11.1CT 版本中启用了分布式快速交换（DFS）功能时存在安全绕过漏洞。当路由器将流量从启用了 DFS 的接口转发至未启用 DFS 的接口时，远程攻击者可绕过特定的访问控制列表（ACL）规则，导致未授权访问受保护的网络资源。该漏洞影响 Cisco IOS 11.1CC 和 11.1CT 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。Cisco 已发布相关修复建议。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1464"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至修复了 CSCdk35564 的版本（11.1CC 和 11.1CT 系列中已修复该缺陷的后续版本）。如无法升级，可在接口上禁用 distributed fast switching（DFS）功能，或确保启用了 DFS 的接口与未启用 DFS 的接口之间流量经过正确的 ACL 检查，避免 ACL 绕过。同时建议在边界路由器上实施最小权限访问控制策略作为纵深防御。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-016.shtml","http://www.cisco.com/warp/public/770/iosdfsacl-pub.shtml","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1401"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1118.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1095","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1095.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1386","title":"Perl 符号链接任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Perl 5.004_04 及更早版本在使用 -e 选项执行脚本时，通过 mktemp 生成临时文件名 /tmp/perl-ea 后接进程 PID，然后以 O_WRONLY|O_CREAT|O_TRUNC 标志打开该文件，但未使用 O_EXCL 标志防止竞态条件。本地攻击者可通过监视目标进程 PID，在文件创建前抢先创建同名符号链接指向任意文件，诱使 Perl 以当前用户权限覆盖或破坏目标文件内容。该漏洞可被用于篡改 /etc/ftpusers、/etc/shadow 等关键系统文件，导致本地权限提升或数据破坏。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1386"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级至 Perl 5.004_05 或更高版本，该版本在 perl.c 中将 open() 调用添加 O_EXCL 标志，防止符号链接竞争攻击。如无法升级，应避免在不可信环境中使用 perl -e 执行脚本，或使用 File::Temp 模块的安全临时文件创建功能替代直接写入 /tmp 目录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=88932165406213&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7243.php","http://www.redhat.com/support/errata/rh50-errata-general.html#perl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1095.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1093","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1093.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1379","title":"DNS 服务器 UDP 查询反射放大拒绝服务漏洞","description":"DNS 协议允许远程攻击者利用 UDP DNS 查询中的伪造源地址将 DNS 服务器作为流量放大器，向受害者发送远超攻击者发出流量的放大流量，导致拒绝服务","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1379"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-31","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"在网络边界部署 ingress 过滤（BCP 38）阻止伪造源地址流量，同时限制 DNS 服务器仅对授权客户端开放递归查询，并对 DNS 响应速率进行限制以缓解放大攻击","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T17:13:49.907973589+00:00","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-063.shtml","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93348057829957&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93433758607623&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7238.php"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1093.toml"}]